text: <@U030TQFR3|ben> has joined the channel
Friends, this guy named Ben just joined your team. I'm that guy. Hello!
Welcome, Ben!
Hi Ben! Looking forward to meeting and working with you!
I'm in the office for a few more minutes if you'd like to say hi. I'm out in the front room.
(I'm currently out, but I'll be back either later today or tomorrow)
I will meet you tomorrow! Looking forward to it.

I met with Marcelino, David and Justin this morning to get familiarized with what came out of the session with the Immersion folks last week. Happy to be on board, stuff looks very cool.

We talked about next step being an initial UX exploration. <@U0260V4K1>,  you wanted to check in with <@U0260V1BX> on that front — do you two want to find each other this afternoon? Or shall I find a time for us all to get together tomorrow morning?
yeah - <@U0260V1BX> what's the rest of you're day look like?
i've got a 3pm call with energous but am otherwise free
we can talk whenever
you want to grab a couple minutes around 2?
sure
Im in the front conference room whenever
hey <@U02F8TTPU> do you have the samsung gear at home with you, or is it at the office?

I will plan on putting the Gear back in that spot whenever I leave
